		<td class=subject><div class="subject">■ SoL VAH のBST Newbieクエスト：もう取り返しはつきませんか</div></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#ffffff">
			<table width="100%" border=0 cellpadding=1 cellspacing=0>
			<tr><td width="1%" nowrap valign=top>投稿者：</td><td width="99%" colspan=2><b>とほほほ</b> さん　　<span style="font-size:80%;">( uid 28084, posts:1, since 2003/02/04 )</span>
